{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act26side_level_act26side_08_beg","storyGroup":"act26side","storySort":17,"storyDependence":"act26side_level_act26side_07_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"HE-8","storyName":"愿跟随主","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"费德里科会为所有待办事项分出优先级，现在最优先的，并非缉捕眼前的阿尔图罗。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act26side/level_act26side_08_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act26side_08","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":15,"next":17,"characters":["修道院主教","阿尔图罗","费德里科","奥伦","里凯莱","蕾缪安","斯普莉雅","克莱芒"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_bg_39_g12_anbandonspace.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":5},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.8","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":10},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":12},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"一切都已经准备好了，众人会在晨会上吃下它......吃下最后一顿餐食。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"你的琴声......会为我感到悲哀吗？还是庆贺？","id":16,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我不懂音乐，阿尔图罗。就像我无法理解你。","id":17,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"你站在这里，我与你共感，但你仿佛一片空白。","id":18,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_490_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我不过是依照我的意愿自由演奏，阁下。我的音乐只是一面镜子。","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_490_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"镜子......呵。","id":22,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c2/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":23},{"type":"charslot","id":24},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_dishes","id":25},{"type":"text","text":"年迈的主教端起瓷盘，双手在琴声中颤抖着。","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"他仿佛在与幽暗中回荡的琴音角力，等待着对方的终结。","id":27},{"type":"text","text":"多年前修道院里响起乐声时，他还很年轻，年轻到在喷泉里的倒影中看不见一根白发。","id":28},{"type":"text","text":"荒野的羽兽被吸引到这片移动的沃土上，在管风琴声中振翅，飞过广场。年迈的老主教将修道院交给他，最年轻的修士斯特凡诺。","id":29},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":32},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“你要留众人活在乐园之中。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":33},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我要如何留众人活在乐园之中？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":34},{"type":"subtitle","id":35},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":36},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":37},{"type":"text","text":"如今历经沧桑的主教托雷格罗萨闭上眼睛。","id":38},{"type":"text","text":"琴音依然回荡着，回荡着，回荡着。然后——","id":39},{"type":"text","text":"他松开了手。","id":40},{"type":"dialog","id":41},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":42},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bottlebroken","id":43},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.7","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":44},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":45},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_490_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......啊。","id":47,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_490_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"多痛苦啊，这就是你的选择。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_490_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":49},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":51},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":52},{"type":"charslot","id":53},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_bg_39_g1_monasteryentrance.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","amount":"0","block":"true","id":55},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":56},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_ponder_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":57,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":58},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":59},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":60},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":61},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":64},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":65},{"type":"text","text":"礼拜堂紧闭的大门里传来模糊的说话声。","id":66},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科站在空旷的大厅中听了片刻，然后转身走上了楼梯。","id":67},{"type":"dialog","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":70},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","id":71},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":72},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......装备正常。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"截至目前，唯一的损失为一枚通讯器。","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"当前目标未更改，继续执行任务。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"已锁定嫌疑人。","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":78},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":80},{"type":"charslot","id":81},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/12/Avg_bg_39_g10_monasterycorridor_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":83},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_footstep_stonestep","volume":"0.8","channel":"alstep","loop":"false","id":84},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"alstep","fadetime":"3.5","id":85},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":86},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":87},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#9$1","duration":"0.5","id":88},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":89},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"里面情况怎么样？","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"圣餐仪式应该已经结束了。","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......情况和我想的一样吗？","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"恐怕是的。","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"该死，费德里科呢？","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"联络不上。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......他知不知道深海教会养出来的怪物有多难对付？","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"工作总是需要人来做。蕾缪安和斯普莉雅呢？","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"收到你的消息之后，她们去地下调查了。","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"好吧，那这最麻烦的工作只能我们两个人来干了。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"推门吧。","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":112},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"charslot","id":116},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8e/Avg_bg_39_g7_chapel.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":119},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_open_door","volume":"1","id":120},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":121},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":122,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":123},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"无论身在何处，无论面对何种境遇，我们都应当彼此尊敬，彼此爱护——","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"——早安，来自圣城的使者。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/00/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"......盘子已经空了。","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"里凯莱，控制住全部居民。我来对付主教。","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"你有什么疑问吗，使者？","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"疑问？倒不如说......阁下为何想不开，非要将这次晨会变成“最后一次”？","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"蕾缪安应该告知过阁下，回到拉特兰对接之后，阁下有很大机会继续担任这座修道院的主教......","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"拉特兰的使者，你们......凭什么来质问我？","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我已做出自己的选择，放弃了所有人都能得救的宏愿。","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"修道院已经穷途末路，最后一次晨会上，就让所有人的盘子空着吧。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我刚刚向众人宣布，安布罗修修道院，同意返回拉特兰。","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......返回拉特兰？","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"阁下该不会认为，我们会放任深海教会......","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"......我说过了，我已做出选择。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"奥伦，他说的是真的。","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"居民们并没有产生变化的迹象。我检查过餐盘了，是干净的。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"是的，我亲手处理了那些怪物的血肉，全部掺进了面包里。","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"不过这批原本用于晨会的面包，我已经锁在了地下的柜子里，以免饥饿的居民误食。","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"如今奥卢斯已经离开，你们担忧的东西不会继续滋生。","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":156},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_key","id":157},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":158},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"这是柜门的钥匙，请你们拿去。这可以证明我所言非虚，你们或许也更清楚如何处置深海教会的赠予。","id":160,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"多谢配合。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"看来今天用不上这把铳了......","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"你该不会觉得遗憾吧？","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"怎么会？","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"我只是松了口气，麻烦的事情终于结束了。接下来的工作该回到正轨了......吧？","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":170},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":171},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.6","id":172},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......蕾缪安，你听到主教说的话了吗？我这就带着钥匙下来。","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/90/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":175},{"type":"charslot","id":176},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.6","id":177},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","name":"avg_npc_925_1#7$1","povX":"-20","style":"cutin","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","offsetx":"0","width":"200","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"不用了。","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"柜子被人砸穿了，里面是空的。","id":180},{"type":"dialog","id":181},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":182},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":183},{"type":"charslot","id":184},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","block":"true","id":185},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_bg_39_g12_anbandonspace.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":186},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1","id":187},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_925_1#6$1","id":188},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":189},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":191},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_925_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"褪色餐巾，地上的瓷盘碎片，其他细节全都和主教的陈述一致呢。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"而且，从之前的记载来看，吃下这些东西的后果是不可逆的......他如果真的已经让人吃下了这些，就没有必要再对我们说谎。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯普莉雅","text":"那就说明有人偷走了这份“圣餐”。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_avg_4015_spuria_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_925_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"我们必须立刻找到这个人。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯普莉雅","text":"呃，在这么大的修道院里找人，是不是有点太困难了？","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_avg_4015_spuria_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_925_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"......","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"我在想，我们好像都忘记了一些事情。","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"比如，杰拉尔德听说了那个萨科塔女孩堕天，这件事给了他很大打击。","id":204,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"但我们绝不可能把堕天的消息传出去，杰拉尔德是如何得知了这件事？","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_925_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"再比如，圣堂的那场火，究竟是怎么回事？","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"如果没有其他人的支持，主教或许也不会如此一意孤行......","id":208,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"在这一切之后，恐怕失望的人不止主教一位。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4015_spuria_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯普莉雅","text":"......我记得，福尔图娜走进礼拜堂时，在场的还有一个人。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_4015_spuria_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":212},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":213},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"charslot","id":215},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":217},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":219},{"type":"subtitle","text":"主教阁下还是做了这样的选择......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":220},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我也不是没有想过，最后事情很可能会变成现在这样。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":221},{"type":"subtitle","text":"主教阁下是个善良的人，这份善良令他怀抱着崇高的理想努力到现在，也使得他在最后一刻败给了软弱。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":222},{"type":"subtitle","text":"而我与他不同。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":223},{"type":"subtitle","text":"在很久很久以前，我就已经不再怀抱希望。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":224},{"type":"subtitle","id":225},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":226},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":227},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":228},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"唔？有客人来了。","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"不得不说，我有些惊讶。虽说给了你提示，但是......","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我还以为根据你的那套理性逻辑判断，你会得出“有其他优先级更高的事项要处理”这种结论。","id":232},{"type":"dialog","id":233},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":234},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"charslot","id":236},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_39_i10.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":238},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"120","yFrom":"50","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"16","block":"false","id":239},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":240,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":241},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我们有多久没见过面了，费德里科？五年，还是六年？","id":244},{"type":"dialog","id":245},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"咦，怎么你不说——“停止这些没有意义的言语，通缉犯阿尔图罗”了？","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"还是说，这次你终于打算换一种打招呼的方式？","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"那不如就像住在我家里的那些年一样......叫我一声姐姐？","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......哦？到了这个地步都没有生气吗？","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"你走进这扇门，竟然没有在看到我的第一时刻动手，这不是你的风格。","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"那就让我来猜猜你现在反常的原因好了。","id":253},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":255},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":256},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cellodoubt","id":257},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"你是在等待什么吗？","id":259},{"type":"dialog","id":260},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":261},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cellodoubth","id":262},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"还是说......你在犹豫什么？","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":265},{"type":"dialog","id":266},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"你听，这座小小的修道院装满了各种各样的声音。","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"悲伤，痛苦，猜疑，嫉恨......还有绝望。","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"所有的声音交织在一起，比任何人为创造出来的旋律都要细腻动人。","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"啊......真是好奇。费德里科·吉亚洛，你感受到什么了吗？到底有没有哪一种音符，能在你那不同于常人的大脑中跃动？","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"通缉犯阿尔图罗，我已对你的言语与行动完成评估。","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"目前我要优先处理的事项不是你。","id":274},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":276},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":278},{"type":"charslot","id":279},{"type":"image","id":280},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_bg_39_g3_abandonsancturay_ex.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":281},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#3$1","id":282},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":283},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act26side/m_avg_cledub_sad.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":285,"musicid":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":286},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"你没有去礼拜堂吗，费德里科先生？","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我以为你和你的同事们的视线都会被主教阁下吸引......","id":289,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你才是主导这一系列异常事件的嫌疑人。","id":291,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"......嗯。","id":293,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我尊重......是的，我尊重主教阁下的选择。","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"所有人都尊敬他、爱戴他，当然会这样，因为我们都在主教阁下的庇护之下......","id":295,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":297,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"这很好理解，对吧？","id":299,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"在你出于各种原因被城市驱逐，只能徘徊在荒野上，认定自己只有死路一条的时候......","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"在你饥肠辘辘，不管朝什么方向走，都只能看到单调绝望的景色，好像永远走不出这片吃人之地的时候......","id":301,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"就在这时候，你跨过一个小坡，越过一块岩石，穿过一条峡谷。","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"你看到尘土的后方，竟然有一座城一样的建筑，里面的人给你端来食物，还让你留在屋子里过夜。","id":303,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"尽管只有一点点粗糙的面包，一碗味道很淡的汤。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"尽管屋子的墙壁有裂缝，总需要修修补补......","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"但你没有在荒野上死去。你被接纳了。","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"所以你们有些人会称这里为“乐园”。","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"“乐园”......然而是虚假的。","id":310,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"在来到这里不久之后，我发现......身边有感染了矿石病的萨卡兹朋友消失了。","id":311,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我找了她很久，才发现......就在这里，在地下有一间房间，听说从前是个训练室，那里的墙壁很结实......","id":312,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"人们会把病得快要不行了的人送去那个房间里。","id":313,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......非专业的防护设备并不能真正有效地阻断源石粉尘传播。","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我们没有别的办法。","id":317,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"或者，你想说那些得了病的人，可以自觉地在生命的最后时刻离开修道院，独自去荒野上等待死亡？","id":318,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我们能做的只有把这些痛苦埋藏在看不见的地方，别过头去，掩住耳朵......我们从来救不了谁，也没有谁能救我们。","id":319,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"可即便是这样虚假的平静，也终究会被打破。","id":320,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"就像现在，你们来了。","id":322,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我们的任务是维系这里的秩序。","id":324,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"当然，这里的生活并不是被你们摧毁的。它只是自然而然地变成了现在的样子。","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"就像我种的花，无论我再怎么精心呵护它，到了它该凋谢的时候，它还是会一点点地变得面目全非。","id":327,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你被阿尔图罗影响了。","id":329,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"你是说阿尔图罗小姐的琴声？","id":331,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"或许吧。从她的琴声里，我常常能听见上面这些回忆。","id":332,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"但她从来没有走进我们的生活。我知道的，她只是把我们的烦恼、我们的痛苦，当作闲暇的点缀......","id":333,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"既然如此，她又怎么可能真的干扰我们的意志，替我们做出这些选择呢？","id":334,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":335},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_pick_lock","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"f","id":336},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"f","fadetime":"1.5","id":337},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":338},{"type":"dialog","id":339},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......检测到危险物品。","id":341,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你在这处圣堂，不，整座修道院的地下藏了大量可燃物。","id":342,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"嗯。","id":344,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"这是一个......可能的选项。","id":345,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"无论你们来还是不来，这座修道院中的平静生活都已经无法延续。","id":346,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"你见过饥饿与对流落荒野的恐惧将人逼到什么地步吗，费德里科先生？","id":347,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"我见过。","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"在事情发展到无可挽回的地步之前......我会终止这一切。","id":349,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":350},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":351},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":352},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunload","volume":"1","id":353},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":354},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"克莱芒·杜波瓦，你涉嫌破坏安布罗修修道院，并与多起发生于此地的牵涉拉特兰公民权益的案件有关。","id":356,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你被确认为拉特兰公证所的执行目标，根据相关条律规定，我会立刻执行抓捕程序。","id":357,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":358},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":359},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":360},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_lighter","volume":"0.3","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"......","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":364},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunshot","volume":"0.9","id":365},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":366},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.4","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":368},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_flapradio","volume":"0.9","id":370},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":371},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#4$1","focus":"none","id":372},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科并不会说出多余的警告。他只会用手中的武器来替代言语。","id":373},{"type":"text","text":"克莱芒并未倒下。","id":374},{"type":"text","text":"消瘦的男人捂着失去知觉的胳膊，惨笑了一下。","id":375},{"type":"dialog","id":376},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"确认点火器已破坏。","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"为什么......不杀死我？","id":380,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"为什么还要费力瞄准点火器？","id":381,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你的行为并未直接导致任何拉特兰公民的死亡。律法并不会宣判你的死刑。","id":383,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_924_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"律法啊......我在这里生活了这么多年，聆听着主教阁下的指引，遵循着你们的律法。","id":385,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"在平时我总能感受到它的约束......可在混乱中，在我们最需要它的时候，它就会消失不见。","id":386,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"从某一个时刻开始，我就只能听到阿尔图罗小姐的琴声了。","id":387,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"费德里科先生，想救我的是拉特兰的律法......还是你自己？","id":388,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_924_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":389},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":390},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":391},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":392},{"type":"charslot","id":393},{"type":"image","id":394}],"characters":["修道院主教","阿尔图罗","费德里科","奥伦","里凯莱","蕾缪安","斯普莉雅","克莱芒"]}